This is parseopt, a collection of POSIX-compatible argument parsing functions.
http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/basedefs/xbd_chap12.html#tag_12_02

parseopt: a helper for shell scripts, works with POSIX sh, dash, bash, mksh, zsh
parseopt.rb: for Ruby
parseopt.tiny.rb: tiny version without error checking, suitable for copy-paste
parseopt.go: for Go

